# Frontend Implementation Plan - NLP Quiz System

The goal is to build a premium, AI-native Next.js 14 frontend for the NLP Quiz Generation System. The UI will follow a modern, dark-mode, glassmorphism aesthetic inspired by Vercel and Linear, utilizing Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, Framer Motion, and Zustand for state management. 

## User Review Required

